Process wise Production Report
query:
select 
	jo.production_order as "Production Order:Link/Production Order:100",
	ifnull(jo.production_order_quantity,0) as "Expected Qty:Data:120",
        ifnull(jo.sales_order,Null) as "Sales Order:Data:120",
	ifnull(sum(case when jo.process='Shearing' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Shearing,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Welding' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Welding,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Cutting' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Cutting,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Cleaning' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Cleaning,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Hot Dip Galvanizing' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as HDG,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Powder Coating' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Powder_Coating,

	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Cleaning' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Cleaning,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Pre Gal Insp' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Pre_Gal_Insp,

	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Wet Coating' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Wet_Coating,
ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Punching' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Punching,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Final Inspection' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Final_Inspection,
	ifnull(sum(jo.rejected_qty),0) as "Rejected Quantity:Data:120"
from `tabJob Order Detail` jo ,`tabJob Card` jc
group by  jo.production_order;

name: Customer Addresses And Contacts
query:
SELECT
	`tabCustomer`.name as "Customer ID:Link/Customer",
	`tabCustomer`.customer_name as "Customer Name",
	`tabCustomer`.customer_group as "Customer Group:Link/Customer Group",
	`tabAddress`.address_line1 as "Address Line 1",
	`tabAddress`.address_line2 as "Address Line 2",
	`tabAddress`.city as "City",
	`tabAddress`.state as "State",
	`tabAddress`.pincode as "Postal Code",
	`tabAddress`.country as "Country",
	`tabAddress`.is_primary_address as "Is Primary Address:Check", 
	`tabContact`.first_name as "First Name",
	`tabContact`.last_name as "Last Name",
	`tabContact`.phone as "Phone",
	`tabContact`.mobile_no as "Mobile No",
	`tabContact`.email_id as "Email Id",
	`tabContact`.is_primary_contact as "Is Primary Contact:Check"
FROM
	`tabCustomer`
	left join `tabAddress` on (
		`tabAddress`.customer=`tabCustomer`.name
	)
	left join `tabContact` on (
		`tabContact`.customer=`tabCustomer`.name
	)
WHERE
	`tabCustomer`.docstatus<2
ORDER BY
	`tabCustomer`.name asc

Ordered Items To Be Billed
query:
select 
 `tabSales Order`.`name` as "Sales Order:Link/Sales Order:120",
 `tabSales Order`.`customer` as "Customer:Link/Customer:120",
  `tabSales Order`.`customer_name` as "Customer Name:150",
`tabSales Order`.`status` as "Status",
 `tabSales Order`.`transaction_date` as "Date:Date",
 `tabSales Order`.`project` as "Project",
 `tabSales Order Item`.item_code as "Item:Link/Item:120",
 `tabSales Order Item`.base_amount as "Amount:Currency:110",
 (`tabSales Order Item`.billed_amt * ifnull(`tabSales Order`.conversion_rate, 1)) as "Billed Amount:Currency:110",
 (`tabSales Order Item`.base_amount - (`tabSales Order Item`.billed_amt * ifnull(`tabSales Order`.conversion_rate, 1))) as "Pending Amount:Currency:120",
 `tabSales Order Item`.item_name as "Item Name::150",
 `tabSales Order Item`.description as "Description::200",
 `tabSales Order`.`company` as "Company:Link/Company:"
from
 `tabSales Order`, `tabSales Order Item`
where
 `tabSales Order Item`.`parent` = `tabSales Order`.`name`
 and `tabSales Order`.docstatus = 1
 and `tabSales Order`.status != "Closed"
 and `tabSales Order Item`.amount > 0
 and `tabSales Order Item`.billed_amt < `tabSales Order Item`.amount
order by `tabSales Order`.transaction_date asc

name: Ordered Items To Be Delivered
query:
select 
 `tabSales Order`.`name` as "Sales Order:Link/Sales Order:120",
 `tabSales Order`.`customer` as "Customer:Link/Customer:120",
 `tabSales Order`.`customer_name` as "Customer Name::150",
 `tabSales Order`.`transaction_date` as "Date:Date",
 `tabSales Order`.`project` as "Project",
 `tabSales Order Item`.item_code as "Item:Link/Item:120",
 `tabSales Order Item`.qty as "Qty:Float:140",
 `tabSales Order Item`.delivered_qty as "Delivered Qty:Float:140",
 (`tabSales Order Item`.qty - ifnull(`tabSales Order Item`.delivered_qty, 0)) as "Qty to Deliver:Float:140",
 `tabSales Order Item`.base_rate as "Rate:Float:140",
 `tabSales Order Item`.base_amount as "Amount:Float:140",
 ((`tabSales Order Item`.qty - ifnull(`tabSales Order Item`.delivered_qty, 0))*`tabSales Order Item`.base_rate) as "Amount to Deliver:Float:140",
 `tabBin`.actual_qty as "Available Qty:Float:120",
 `tabBin`.projected_qty as "Projected Qty:Float:120",
 `tabSales Order`.`delivery_date` as "Expected Delivery Date:Date:120",
 `tabSales Order Item`.item_name as "Item Name::150",
 `tabSales Order Item`.description as "Description::200",
 `tabSales Order Item`.item_group as "Item Group:Link/Item Group:120",
 `tabSales Order Item`.warehouse as "Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:200"
from
 `tabSales Order` JOIN `tabSales Order Item` 
 LEFT JOIN `tabBin` ON (`tabBin`.item_code = `tabSales Order Item`.item_code
 and `tabBin`.warehouse = `tabSales Order Item`.warehouse)
where
 `tabSales Order Item`.`parent` = `tabSales Order`.`name`
 and `tabSales Order`.docstatus = 1
 and `tabSales Order`.status not in ("Stopped", "Closed")
 and ifnull(`tabSales Order Item`.delivered_qty,0) < ifnull(`tabSales Order Item`.qty,0)
order by `tabSales Order`.transaction_date asc

query:

        po_item.item_group as "Item Group:Link/Item Group:120",
	po_item.description as "Description::150",

	po_item.uom as "UOM:Link/UOM:80",
	po_item.base_rate as "Rate:Currency:120",

	po.name as "Purchase Order:Link/Purchase Order:120",
	po.transaction_date as "Transaction Date:Date:140",
	po.supplier as "Supplier:Link/Supplier:130",
        sup.supplier_name as "Supplier Name::150",

	ifnull(po_item.received_qty, 0) as "Received Qty:Float:120",

name: Issued Items Against Production Order
query:
select
    ste.production_order as "Production Order:Link/Production Order:120",
    ste.posting_date as "Issue Date:Date:140",
    ste_item.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:120",
	ste_item.description as "Description::150",
	ste_item.transfer_qty as "Qty:Float:100",
	ste_item.stock_uom as "UOM:Link/UOM:80",
	ste_item.amount as "Amount:Currency:120",
	ste_item.serial_no as "Serial No:Link/Serial No:80",
	ste_item.s_warehouse as "Source Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:120",
	ste_item.t_warehouse as "Target Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:120",
	pro.production_item as "Finished Goods:Link/Item:120", 
	ste.name as "Stock Entry:Link/Stock Entry:120",
	ste.company as "Company:Link/Company:",
	(select bin.projected_qty from `tabBin` bin 
			where  bin.item_code= ste_item.item_code and bin.warehouse= ste_item.s_warehouse) as "Projected Quantity as Source:Float:200"
from	`tabStock Entry` ste, `tabStock Entry Detail` ste_item, `tabProduction Order` pro
where
	ifnull(ste.production_order, '') != '' and ste.name = ste_item.parent 
	and ste.production_order = pro.name and ste.docstatus = 1
	and ste.purpose = 'Material Transfer for Manufacture'
order by ste.posting_date, ste.production_order, ste_item.item_code

name: Sales Partners Commission
query:
SELECT
    sales_partner as "Sales Partner:Link/Sales Partner:150",
	sum(base_net_total) as "Invoiced Amount (Exculsive Tax):Currency:210",
	sum(total_commission) as "Total Commission:Currency:150",
	sum(total_commission)*100/sum(base_net_total) as "Average Commission Rate:Currency:170"
FROM
	`tabSales Invoice`
WHERE
	docstatus = 1 and ifnull(base_net_total, 0) > 0 and ifnull(total_commission, 0) > 0
GROUP BY
	sales_partner
ORDER BY
	"Total Commission:Currency:120"

name: Requested Items To Be Ordered
query:
select 
    mr.name as "Material Request:Link/Material Request:120",
	mr.transaction_date as "Date:Date:100",
	mr_item.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:120",
	sum(ifnull(mr_item.qty, 0)) as "Qty:Float:100",
	sum(ifnull(mr_item.ordered_qty, 0)) as "Ordered Qty:Float:100", 
	(sum(mr_item.qty) - sum(ifnull(mr_item.ordered_qty, 0))) as "Qty to Order:Float:100",
	mr_item.item_name as "Item Name::150",
	mr_item.description as "Description::200",
	mr.company as "Company:Link/Company:"
from
	`tabMaterial Request` mr, `tabMaterial Request Item` mr_item
where
	mr_item.parent = mr.name
	and mr.material_request_type = "Purchase"
	and mr.docstatus = 1
	and mr.status != "Stopped"
group by mr.name, mr_item.item_code
having
	sum(ifnull(mr_item.ordered_qty, 0)) < sum(ifnull(mr_item.qty, 0))
order by mr.transaction_date asc

name: Pending SO Items For Purchase Request
query:

 so_item.description as "Description::120",
 so.`name` as "S.O. No.:Link/Sales Order:120",

 mr.name as "Material Request:Link/Material Request:120",

  `tabProduction Order`.creation as "Date:Date:120",
  `tabProduction Order`.production_item as "Item:Link/Item:150",
  `tabProduction Order`.qty as "To Produce:Int:100",
  `tabProduction Order`.produced_qty as "Produced:Int:100",
  `tabProduction Order`.company as "Company:Link/Company:"
FROM
  `tabProduction Order`
WHERE
  `tabProduction Order`.docstatus=1
  AND ifnull(`tabProduction Order`.produced_qty,0) = `tabProduction Order`.qty

name: Item Shortage Report
query:
SELECT  bin.warehouse as "Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:150",
	bin.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:100",
	bin.actual_qty as "Actual Quantity:Float:120",
	bin.ordered_qty as "Ordered Quantity:Float:120",
	bin.planned_qty as "Planned Quantity:Float:120",
	bin.reserved_qty as "Reserved Quantity:Float:120",
	bin.projected_qty as "Projected Quantity:Float:120",
	item.item_name as "Item Name:Data:150",
	item.description as "Description::200"
FROM tabBin as bin
INNER JOIN tabItem as item
ON bin.item_code=item.name
WHERE bin.projected_qty<0
ORDER BY bin.projected_qty;

name: Items To Be Requested
query:
SELECT
    tabBin.item_code as "Item:Link/Item:120",
    tabBin.warehouse as "Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:120",
    tabBin.actual_qty as "Actual:Float:90",
    tabBin.indented_qty as "Requested:Float:90",
    tabBin.reserved_qty as "Reserved:Float:90",
    tabBin.ordered_qty as "Ordered:Float:90",
    tabBin.projected_qty as "Projected:Float:90"
FROM
    tabBin, tabItem
WHERE
    tabBin.item_code = tabItem.name
   AND tabBin.projected_qty < 0
ORDER BY
    tabBin.projected_qty ASC

Supplier Addresses and Contacts
query:
SELECT
    `tabSupplier`.name as "Supplier:Link/Supplier:120",
	`tabSupplier`.supplier_name as "Supplier Name::120",
	`tabSupplier`.supplier_type as "Supplier Type:Link/Supplier Type:120",
	concat_ws(', ', 
		trim(',' from `tabAddress`.address_line1), 
		trim(',' from tabAddress.address_line2), 
		tabAddress.state, tabAddress.pincode, tabAddress.country
	) as 'Address::180',
    concat_ws(', ', `tabContact`.first_name, `tabContact`.last_name) as "Contact Name::180",
	`tabContact`.phone as "Phone",
	`tabContact`.mobile_no as "Mobile No",
	`tabContact`.email_id as "Email Id::120",
	`tabContact`.is_primary_contact as "Is Primary Contact::120"
FROM
	`tabSupplier`
	left join `tabAddress` on (
		`tabAddress`.supplier=`tabSupplier`.name
	)
	left join `tabContact` on (
		`tabContact`.supplier=`tabSupplier`.name
	)
WHERE
	`tabSupplier`.docstatus<2
ORDER BY
	`tabSupplier`.name asc

name: Lead Details
query:
SELECT
    `tabLead`.name as "Lead Id:Link/Lead:120",
    `tabLead`.lead_name as "Lead Name::120",
	`tabLead`.company_name as "Company Name::120",
	`tabLead`.status as "Status::120",
	concat_ws(', ', 
		trim(',' from `tabAddress`.address_line1), 
		trim(',' from tabAddress.address_line2)
	) as 'Address::180',
	`tabAddress`.state as "State::100",
	`tabAddress`.pincode as "Pincode::70",
	`tabAddress`.country as "Country::100",
	`tabLead`.phone as "Phone::100",
	`tabLead`.mobile_no as "Mobile No::100",
	`tabLead`.email_id as "Email Id::120",
	`tabLead`.lead_owner as "Lead Owner::120",
	`tabLead`.source as "Source::120",
	`tabLead`.territory as "Territory::120",
    `tabLead`.owner as "Owner:Link/User:120"
FROM
	`tabLead`
	left join `tabAddress` on (
		`tabAddress`.lead=`tabLead`.name
	)
WHERE
	`tabLead`.docstatus<2
ORDER BY
	`tabLead`.name asc

name: Production Report (Process Wise)
query:
select 
	jo.production_order as "Production Order:Link/Production Order:100",
	ifnull(jo.production_order_quantity,0) as "Expected Qty:Data:120",
    ifnull(jo.sales_order,Null) as "Sales Order:Data:120",
	ifnull(sum(case when jo.process='Programming' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Programming,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Punching' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Punching,
	ifnull(sum(case when jo.process='Shearing' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Shearing,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Cutting' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Cutting,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Bending' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Bending,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Reduced Bending' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Reduced_Bending,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Pre Inspection' and jo.black_material='Yes' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Pre_Insp_Black,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Pre Inspection' and jo.black_material='No' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Pre_Insp,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Welding' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Welding,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Hot Dip Galvanizing' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as HDG,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Powder Coating' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Powder_Coating,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Wet Coating' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Wet_Coating,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Cleaning' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Cleaning,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Drilling' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Drilling,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Tapping' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Tapping,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Rolling' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Rolling,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Assembly' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Assembly,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Custom 1' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Custom_1,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Custom 2' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Custom_2,
	ifnull(sum(case when  jo.process='Final Inspection' then  jo.completed_job else 0 end),0) as Final_Inspection,
	(select sum(jo.rejected_qty) from `tabJob Order Detail` group by jo.production_order ) as "Rejected Quantity:Data:120"
from `tabJob Order Detail` jo
group by  jo.production_order;

name: EMI Stock Balance
query:
select
sle.item_code as "Item Name",
sle.stock_uom as "UOM",
ifnull(case when  sle.voucher_type='Purchase Receipt' or(sle.voucher_type='Stock Entry' and se.purpose='Material Receipt') then  sle.actual_qty else 0 end,0) as InQty,
ifnull(case when  sle.voucher_type='Delivery Note' then  sle.actual_qty else 0 end,0) as OutQty,
sle.actual_qty as "Qty",
sle.valuation_rate as "Valuation Rate",
sle.warehouse as "Warehouse",
sle.voucher_type as "Reference Type",
sle.voucher_no as "Reference No",
ifnull((case when sle.voucher_type='Delivery Note' then dni.against_sales_order else 0 end),0) as Sales_Order,
ifnull((case when sle.voucher_type='Purchase Receipt' then pri.purchase_order else 0 end),0) as Purchase_Order,
sle.posting_date as "Date"
from
`tabStock Ledger Entry` as sle left join `tabStock Entry` as se ON sle.voucher_no=se.name
left join `tabPurchase Receipt Item` pri on sle.voucher_no=pri.parent
left join `tabDelivery Note Item` dni on sle.voucher_detail_no=dni.name
